{"name":"Last Life’s Memories","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 3rd level, you recall fragmented memories from one of the creatures whose body you are made up of. Choose a skill or two tools. You gain proficiency in that skill or with those tools.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Curse of the Created","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/jean-homebrew/images/shaman/Shamanskill_05.png","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ynNsRVwxyMa4aV73"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674884455160,"modifiedTime":1674884897978,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"NnQsixp9PAV6arZU"}
{"name":"Shocking Strike","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Also at 3rd level, once per turn when you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack, you can deal an additional 1d6 lightning damage to the target. When you do, until the end of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on all attack rolls against creatures other than you.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"","subtype":""},"requirements":"Curse of the Created","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/jean-homebrew/images/shaman/Shamanskill_26.png","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.zNO5mRH1njl7AfpP"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674884488628,"modifiedTime":1674884910215,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"RCZYJbEWW4koDSuB"}
{"name":"Electric Charge","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 11th level, you gain resistance to lightning damage. Immediately after you take lightning damage, you gain that many temporary hit points. You lose any remaining temporary hit points from this feature after 1 minute. </p><p>In addition, when you deal damage with a melee weapon attack while you have temporary hit points, you can choose to expend a number of your temporary hit points up to half your accursed level. When you do, the melee weapon attack deals additional lightning damage equal to the temporary hit points expended.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Curse of the Created","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/lightning/orb-ball-purple.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.QvHje0CwAKx4WdVx"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674884560614,"modifiedTime":1674884964223,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"FIE3zAmdA7bUPLdB"}
{"name":"Reassemble Corpus","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 15th level, the maximum value of your Strength, Dexterity, and Constitution scores increases from 20 to 22.</p><p>In addition, each time you finish a long rest, you can choose to decrease your Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution ability score by 2 to increase your Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution ability score by 2, to a maximum of 22.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Curse of the Created","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/skills/social/intimidation-impressing.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.EVq9JGnYEZSCCaGC"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674884636688,"modifiedTime":1674884983310,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"w3HsySzg3d6fraLp"}
{"name":"Stolen Spark","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 20th level, you can use a bonus action to grasp at the spark of eternal life. When you do, you gain the following benefits for the next minute:</p><ul><li><p>The additional lightning damage from your Shocking Strike feature increases to 1d12.</p></li><li><p>At the start of each of your turns, you regain 5 hit points and gain 10 temporary hit points.</p></li><li><p>You gain a +1 bonus to all attack rolls, ability checks, and saving throws that add your Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution modifier.</p></li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you must finish a long rest before you can use it again. You regain the use of this feature early if you use the reaction granted by your It’s Alive! feature.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"type":{"value":"class","subtype":""},"requirements":"Curse of the Created","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/lightning/projectile-tendrils-teal.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.K8IA9gr5KozcBNjw"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674884693490,"modifiedTime":1674885004866,"lastModifiedBy":"B0DJHUzhCGludWuM"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"5OHUZHryL32SpzmP"}
{"name":"Curse of the Created","type":"subclass","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You were not born, nor were you cursed. Instead, you lurched to life with electricity crackling in the air around you. Your creator intended you to be a perfect specimen of their own kind, but when the stitched together corpses you’re made of gained sentience, you were only a grotesque facsimile of true life. Your presence is deeply unsettling to others, including your creator, who may have abandoned you shortly after your animation. Despite their persistent rejections, you long to find a place among other humanoids, though you sometimes wonder if you aren’t more like the monster they see you as...</p><hr /><table class=\"tg\"><thead><tr><th class=\"tg-0v2r\"><p>Level<br /></p></th><th class=\"tg-0v2r\">Curse Features</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"tg-0pky\">1st</td><td class=\"tg-0pky\">@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.3b2Pa5s9LiGaHCyy]{Armed and Angry} @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.9Cfn8yfHdoQba1Ss]{Created Ailments} @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.VRVVYsZY9RjNi6ac]{It’s Alive!}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"tg-0pky\">2nd</td><td class=\"tg-0pky\">@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.zpRw3NQakwzCbSQF]{Created Curse Spells}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"tg-0pky\">3rd</td><td class=\"tg-0pky\">@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.NnQsixp9PAV6arZU]{Last Life’s Memories} @UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.RCZYJbEWW4koDSuB]{Shocking Strike}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"tg-0pky\">5th</td><td class=\"tg-0pky\">@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.TRo9UYYTFjfkgqzX]{Extra Attack}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"tg-0pky\">11th</td><td class=\"tg-0pky\">@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.FIE3zAmdA7bUPLdB]{Electric Charge}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"tg-0lax\">15th</td><td class=\"tg-0lax\">@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.w3HsySzg3d6fraLp]{Reassemble Corpus}</td></tr><tr><td class=\"tg-0lax\">20th</td><td class=\"tg-0lax\">@UUID[Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.5OHUZHryL32SpzmP]{Stolen Spark}</td></tr></tbody></table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"UAH","identifier":"curse-of-the-created","classIdentifier":"accursed","advancement":[{"_id":"y7efuUkqOlup28Q4","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.9Cfn8yfHdoQba1Ss","Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.VRVVYsZY9RjNi6ac","Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.3b2Pa5s9LiGaHCyy"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":1,"title":"Feature"},{"_id":"jLzUJsH4JRExdLWf","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.zpRw3NQakwzCbSQF"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":2,"title":"Features"},{"_id":"WYV2pxP0ARgKOXxL","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.NnQsixp9PAV6arZU","Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.RCZYJbEWW4koDSuB"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":3,"title":"Features"},{"_id":"mHDswbvXZ63SM0BQ","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.TRo9UYYTFjfkgqzX"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":5,"title":"Features"},{"_id":"jjltNve4NkOw7m4c","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.FIE3zAmdA7bUPLdB"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":11,"title":"Features"},{"_id":"P0tay6HPucQFphPm","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.w3HsySzg3d6fraLp"],"optional":false,"spell":{"ability":"","preparation":"","uses":{"max":"","per":""}}},"value":{},"level":15,"title":"Features"},{"_id":"c9mtWavIptuerPyU","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.jean-homebrew.accursed.5OHUZHryL32SpzmP"],"optional":false,"